# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  TVer Downloader — Environment Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#  PROXY SETUP
#  ───────────
#  TVer.jp is geo-restricted to Japan. To download videos outside Japan,
#  you MUST provide a Japanese proxy or use a VPN with a Japanese IP.
#
#  Supported proxy formats:
#
#    HTTP proxy:
#      TVER_PROXY=http://host:port
#      TVER_PROXY=http://username:password@host:port
#
#    HTTPS proxy:
#      TVER_PROXY=https://host:port
#      TVER_PROXY=https://username:password@host:port
#
#    SOCKS5 proxy (recommended for speed):
#      TVER_PROXY=socks5://host:port
#      TVER_PROXY=socks5://username:password@host:port
#
#  Example (SOCKS5 with authentication):
#    TVER_PROXY=socks5://erdevelopmentandfun0tEIo:ToEP8Ues6L@14.137.246.47:50101
#
#  To disable proxy, leave the value empty or comment out the line:
#    TVER_PROXY=
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

TVER_PROXY=socks5://erdevelopmentandfun0tEIo:ToEP8Ues6L@14.137.246.47:50101
